💻 Setup / Installation Instructions

To use My Matcha Study Planner on a laptop or desktop:

1. Open the official My Matcha Study Planner website using any modern web browser.


2. Create a new account or log in with your existing credentials.


3. Purchase a Premium Subscription to unlock all features, including adaptive study planning, analytics, rewards, and collaboration tools.


4. After successful payment, you will gain access to the full web application.


5. (Optional) Download the desktop version available for Windows, macOS, or Linux from the website.


6. Install the application by following the on-screen instructions.


7. Launch the application and sign in to start using your personalized study planner.



System Requirements

Windows 10/11, macOS, or Linux

Google Chrome, Microsoft Edge, Firefox, or Safari (latest version)

Stable internet connection

Active Premium subscription


After setup, users can access all features including task management, adaptive Pomodoro sessions, mood tracking, revision analysis, friend collaboration, character customization, and immersive study environments such as the Library, Coffee Shop, and Japanese Café. 🍵📚✨
